  nnoremap <silent> <buffer> == :Scratch<CR>
  nnoremap <silent> <buffer> =" :Scratch<Bar>put<Bar>1delete _<Bar>filetype detect<CR>
  nnoremap <silent> <buffer> =* :Scratch<Bar>put *<Bar>1delete _<Bar>filetype detect<CR>
